*******************************
* Version 0.4.2 (Aug 2015)    *
*******************************
+ phantom days in classic layout (days from prev/next month) [--phantom-days]

*******************************
* Version 0.4.1 (Nov 2014)    *
*******************************
+ packaging support for Python/Arch Linux {Nick}
! calmagick: fixed bug regarding --min-size being greater than --max-size
* refactored some common code between callirhoe and calmagick

*******************************
* Version 0.4.0 (Oct 2014)    *
*******************************
+ calmagick: combining callirhoe with ImageMagick for impressive
  photo calendars featuring:
    - translucent overlays
    - automatic minimal-entropy overlay placement
    - automatic maximal-entropy cropping (smart-crop)
    - multi-threaded operation, photo globbing, randomizing...

*******************************
* Version 0.3.0 (Sep 2014)    * 
*******************************

+ holiday support (with Orthodox & Catholic Easter based holidays)
+ fully documented code
* code refactoring, better layout separation
+ sparse layout and minor patches {Neels}
+ more languages: german, turkish

*******************************
* Version 0.2.1 (Aug 2012)    * 
*******************************

first "release" (via svn)


